<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Premium Family Plan | CloyMusic</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/FooterPages.css">
</head>
<body>
    <%- include("navbar") %>

    <main class="container premium-page">
        <section class="hero">
            <h1>Music for the Whole Family</h1>
            <p>Up to 6 accounts. One low price. Each member gets their own private Premium experience.</p>
            <a href="#" class="button">Start Family Plan</a>
        </section>

        <section class="features">
            <h2>What’s Included</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>6 Premium Accounts:</strong> One plan. Six individual logins.</li>
                <li><strong>Ad-Free for All:</strong> Everyone enjoys uninterrupted music.</li>
                <li><strong>Offline Listening:</strong> Each user can download and go.</li>
                <li><strong>Parental Controls:</strong> Manage explicit content filters and access.</li>
                <li><strong>Family Mix:</strong> A shared playlist curated from the family’s favorites.</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="pricing">
            <h2>Pricing</h2>
            <p><strong>$4.49/month</strong> — One simple payment. No extra fees.</p>
            <p>Eligible for households of up to 6 people living at the same address.</p>
        </section>

        <section class="why-family">
            <h2>Perfect for Households</h2>
            <div class="grid">
                <div>
                    <h3>Individual Profiles</h3>
                    <p>No shared history. Everyone has their own playlists and preferences.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3>Control & Safety</h3>
                    <p>Manage what younger listeners can hear with our safety settings.</p>
                </div>
                <div>
                    <h3>Fun Together</h3>
                    <p>Family Mix updates weekly with everyone’s top tracks — great for car rides, game nights, and bonding time.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="faq">
            <h2>FAQ</h2>
            <div>
                <h3>Can family members live in different places?</h3>
                <p>No, all accounts must be part of the same household address.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>How are payments handled?</h3>
                <p>Only the plan manager is charged. Other members use their accounts for free.</p>
            </div>
            <div>
                <h3>Can I switch to Family from Individual?</h3>
                <p>Yes! Upgrade anytime from your account settings without losing saved music.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="cta">
            <h2>Bring the Family Together With Music</h2>
            <a href="#" class="button">Start Family Plan</a>
        </section>
    </main>

    <%- include("footer") %>
